150    {

152
153        if (!empty($this->mpdf->title)) {

155        }
156
157        if (!empty($this->mpdf->subject)) {
158            $this->writer->write('/Subject ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($this->mpdf->subject));
159        }
160
161        if (!empty($this->mpdf->author)) {
162            $this->writer->write('/Author ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($this->mpdf->author));
163        }
164
165        if (!empty($this->mpdf->keywords)) {
166            $this->writer->write('/Keywords ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($this->mpdf->keywords));
167        }
168
169        if (!empty($this->mpdf->creator)) {
170            $this->writer->write('/Creator ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($this->mpdf->creator));
171        }
172
173        foreach ($this->mpdf->customProperties as $key => $value) {
174            $this->writer->write('/' . $key . ' ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($value));
175        }
176
177        $now = PdfDate::format(time());
178        $this->writer->write('/CreationDate ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . $now));
179        $this->writer->write('/ModDate ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . $now));
180        if ($this->mpdf->PDFX) {
181            $this->writer->write('/Trapped/False');
182            $this->writer->write('/GTS_PDFXVersion(PDF/X-1a:2003)');
183        }

259    public function writeAssociatedFiles() // _putAssociatedFiles
260    {
261        if (!function_exists('gzcompress')) {
262            throw new \Mpdf\MpdfException('ext-zlib is required for compression of associated files');
263        }
264
265        // for each file, we create the spec object + the stream object
266        foreach ($this->mpdf->associatedFiles as $k => $file) {
267            // spec
268            $this->writer->object();
269            $this->mpdf->associatedFiles[$k]['_root'] = $this->mpdf->n; // we store the root ref of object for future reference (e.g. /EmbeddedFiles catalog)
270            $this->writer->write('<</F ' . $this->writer->string($file['name']));
271            if ($file['description']) {
272                $this->writer->write('/Desc ' . $this->writer->string($file['description']));
273            }
274            $this->writer->write('/Type /Filespec');
275            $this->writer->write('/EF <<');
276            $this->writer->write('/F ' . ($this->mpdf->n + 1) . ' 0 R');
277            $this->writer->write('/UF ' . ($this->mpdf->n + 1) . ' 0 R');
278            $this->writer->write('>>');
279            if ($file['AFRelationship']) {
280                $this->writer->write('/AFRelationship /' . $file['AFRelationship']);
281            }
282            $this->writer->write('/UF ' . $this->writer->string($file['name']));
283            $this->writer->write('>>');
284            $this->writer->write('endobj');
285
286            $fileContent = null;
287            if (isset($file['path'])) {
288                $fileContent = @file_get_contents($file['path']);
289            } elseif (isset($file['content'])) {
290                $fileContent = $file['content'];
291            }
292
293            if (!$fileContent) {
294                throw new \Mpdf\MpdfException(sprintf('Cannot access associated file - %s', $file['path']));
295            }
296
297            $filestream = gzcompress($fileContent);
298            $this->writer->object();
299            $this->writer->write('<</Type /EmbeddedFile');
300            if ($file['mime']) {
301                $this->writer->write('/Subtype /' . $this->writer->escapeSlashes($file['mime']));
302            }
303            $this->writer->write('/Length ' . strlen($filestream));
304            $this->writer->write('/Filter /FlateDecode');
305            if (isset($file['path'])) {
306                $this->writer->write('/Params <</ModDate '.$this->writer->string('D:' . PdfDate::format(filemtime($file['path']))).' >>');
307            } else {
308                $this->writer->write('/Params <</ModDate '.$this->writer->string('D:' . PdfDate::format(time())).' >>');
309            }
310
311            $this->writer->write('>>');
312            $this->writer->stream($filestream);
313            $this->writer->write('endobj');
314        }
315
316        // AF array
317        $this->writer->object();
318        $refs = [];
319        foreach ($this->mpdf->associatedFiles as $file) {
320            $refs[] = '' . $file['_root'] . ' 0 R';
321        }
322        $this->writer->write('[' . implode(' ', $refs) . ']');
323        $this->writer->write('endobj');
324
325        $this->mpdf->associatedFilesRoot = $this->mpdf->n;
326    }

328    public function writeCatalog() //_putcatalog
329    {
330        $this->writer->write('/Type /Catalog');
331        $this->writer->write('/Pages 1 0 R');
332
333        if (is_string($this->mpdf->currentLang)) {
334            $this->writer->write(sprintf('/Lang (%s)', $this->mpdf->currentLang));
335        } elseif (is_string($this->mpdf->default_lang)) {
336            $this->writer->write(sprintf('/Lang (%s)', $this->mpdf->default_lang));
337        }
338
339        if ($this->mpdf->ZoomMode === 'fullpage') {
340            $this->writer->write('/OpenAction [3 0 R /Fit]');
341        } elseif ($this->mpdf->ZoomMode === 'fullwidth') {
342            $this->writer->write('/OpenAction [3 0 R /FitH null]');
343        } elseif ($this->mpdf->ZoomMode === 'real') {
344            $this->writer->write('/OpenAction [3 0 R /XYZ null null 1]');
345        } elseif (!is_string($this->mpdf->ZoomMode)) {
346            $this->writer->write('/OpenAction [3 0 R /XYZ null null ' . ($this->mpdf->ZoomMode / 100) . ']');
347        } elseif ($this->mpdf->ZoomMode === 'none') {
348            // do not write any zoom mode / OpenAction
349        } else {
350            $this->writer->write('/OpenAction [3 0 R /XYZ null null null]');
351        }
352
353        if ($this->mpdf->LayoutMode === 'single') {
354            $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /SinglePage');
355        } elseif ($this->mpdf->LayoutMode === 'continuous') {
356            $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /OneColumn');
357        } elseif ($this->mpdf->LayoutMode === 'twoleft') {
358            $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /TwoColumnLeft');
359        } elseif ($this->mpdf->LayoutMode === 'tworight') {
360            $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /TwoColumnRight');
361        } elseif ($this->mpdf->LayoutMode === 'two') {
362            if ($this->mpdf->mirrorMargins) {
363                $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /TwoColumnRight');
364            } else {
365                $this->writer->write('/PageLayout /TwoColumnLeft');
366            }
367        }
368
369        // Bookmarks
370        if (count($this->mpdf->BMoutlines) > 0) {
371            $this->writer->write('/Outlines ' . $this->mpdf->OutlineRoot . ' 0 R');
372            $this->writer->write('/PageMode /UseOutlines');
373        }
374
375        // Fullscreen
376        if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'FullScreen'))) {
377            $this->writer->write('/PageMode /FullScreen');
378        }
379
380        // Metadata
381        if ($this->mpdf->PDFA || $this->mpdf->PDFX) {
382            $this->writer->write('/Metadata ' . $this->mpdf->MetadataRoot . ' 0 R');
383        }
384
385        // OutputIntents
386        if ($this->mpdf->PDFA || $this->mpdf->PDFX || $this->mpdf->ICCProfile) {
387            $this->writer->write('/OutputIntents [' . $this->mpdf->OutputIntentRoot . ' 0 R]');
388        }
389
390        // Associated files
391        if ($this->mpdf->associatedFilesRoot) {
392            $this->writer->write('/AF '. $this->mpdf->associatedFilesRoot .' 0 R');
393
394            $names = [];
395            foreach ($this->mpdf->associatedFiles as $file) {
396                $names[] = $this->writer->string($file['name']) . ' ' . $file['_root'] . ' 0 R';
397            }
398            $this->writer->write('/Names << /EmbeddedFiles << /Names [' . implode(' ', $names) .  '] >> >>');
399        }
400
401        // Forms
402        if (count($this->form->forms) > 0) {
403            $this->form->_putFormsCatalog();
404        }
405
406        if ($this->mpdf->js !== null) {
407            $this->writer->write('/Names << /JavaScript ' . $this->mpdf->n_js . ' 0 R >> ');
408        }
409
410        if ($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences || $this->mpdf->directionality === 'rtl' || $this->mpdf->mirrorMargins) {
411
412            $this->writer->write('/ViewerPreferences<<');
413
414            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'HideMenubar'))) {
415                $this->writer->write('/HideMenubar true');
416            }
417
418            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'HideToolbar'))) {
419                $this->writer->write('/HideToolbar true');
420            }
421
422            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'HideWindowUI'))) {
423                $this->writer->write('/HideWindowUI true');
424            }
425
426            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'DisplayDocTitle'))) {
427                $this->writer->write('/DisplayDocTitle true');
428            }
429
430            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'CenterWindow'))) {
431                $this->writer->write('/CenterWindow true');
432            }
433
434            if (is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'FitWindow'))) {
435                $this->writer->write('/FitWindow true');
436            }
437
438            // PrintScaling is PDF 1.6 spec.
439            if (!$this->mpdf->PDFA && !$this->mpdf->PDFX && is_int(strpos($this->mpdf->DisplayPreferences, 'NoPrintScaling'))) {
440                $this->writer->write('/PrintScaling /None');
441            }
442
443            if ($this->mpdf->directionality === 'rtl') {
444                $this->writer->write('/Direction /R2L');
445            }
446
447            // Duplex is PDF 1.7 spec.
448            if ($this->mpdf->mirrorMargins && !$this->mpdf->PDFA && !$this->mpdf->PDFX) {
449                // if ($this->mpdf->DefOrientation=='P') $this->writer->write('/Duplex /DuplexFlipShortEdge');
450                $this->writer->write('/Duplex /DuplexFlipLongEdge'); // PDF v1.7+
451            }
452
453            $this->writer->write('>>');
454        }
455
456        if ($this->mpdf->open_layer_pane && ($this->mpdf->hasOC || count($this->mpdf->layers))) {
457            $this->writer->write('/PageMode /UseOC');
458        }
459
460        if ($this->mpdf->hasOC || count($this->mpdf->layers)) {
461
462            $p = $v = $h = $l = $loff = $lall = $as = '';
463
464            if ($this->mpdf->hasOC) {
465
466                if (($this->mpdf->hasOC & 1) === 1) {
467                    $p = $this->mpdf->n_ocg_print . ' 0 R';
468                }
469
470                if (($this->mpdf->hasOC & 2) === 2) {
471                    $v = $this->mpdf->n_ocg_view . ' 0 R';
472                }
473
474                if (($this->mpdf->hasOC & 4) === 4) {
475                    $h = $this->mpdf->n_ocg_hidden . ' 0 R';
476                }
477
478                $as = "<</Event /Print /OCGs [$p $v $h] /Category [/Print]>> <</Event /View /OCGs [$p $v $h] /Category [/View]>>";
479            }
480
481            if (count($this->mpdf->layers)) {
482                foreach ($this->mpdf->layers as $k => $layer) {
483                    if (isset($this->mpdf->layerDetails[$k]) && strtolower($this->mpdf->layerDetails[$k]['state']) === 'hidden') {
484                        $loff .= $layer['n'] . ' 0 R ';
485                    } else {
486                        $l .= $layer['n'] . ' 0 R ';
487                    }
488                    $lall .= $layer['n'] . ' 0 R ';
489                }
490            }
491
492            $this->writer->write("/OCProperties <</OCGs [$p $v $h $lall] /D <</ON [$p $l] /OFF [$v $h $loff] ");
493            $this->writer->write("/Order [$v $p $h $lall] ");
494
495            if ($as) {
496                $this->writer->write("/AS [$as] ");
497            }
498
499            $this->writer->write('>>>>');
500        }
501    }
502
503    /**
504     * @since 5.7.2
505     */
506    public function writeAnnotations() // _putannots
507    {
508        $nb = $this->mpdf->page;
509
510        for ($n = 1; $n <= $nb; $n++) {
511
512            if (isset($this->mpdf->PageLinks[$n]) || isset($this->mpdf->PageAnnots[$n]) || count($this->form->forms) > 0) {
513
514                $wPt = $this->mpdf->pageDim[$n]['w'] * Mpdf::SCALE;
515                $hPt = $this->mpdf->pageDim[$n]['h'] * Mpdf::SCALE;
516
517                // Links
518                if (isset($this->mpdf->PageLinks[$n])) {
519
520                    foreach ($this->mpdf->PageLinks[$n] as $key => $pl) {
521
522                        $this->writer->object();
523                        $annot = '';
524
525                        $rect = sprintf('%.3F %.3F %.3F %.3F', $pl[0], $pl[1], $pl[0] + $pl[2], $pl[1] - $pl[3]);
526
527                        $annot .= '<</Type /Annot /Subtype /Link /Rect [' . $rect . ']';
528                        // Removed as causing undesired effects in Chrome PDF viewer https://github.com/mpdf/mpdf/issues/283
529                        // $annot .= ' /Contents ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($pl[4]);
530                        $annot .= ' /NM ' . $this->writer->string(sprintf('%04u-%04u', $n, $key));
531                        $annot .= ' /M ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . date('YmdHis'));
532
533                        $annot .= ' /Border [0 0 0]';
534
535                        // Use this (instead of /Border) to specify border around link
536
537                        // $annot .= ' /BS <</W 1';    // Width on points; 0 = no line
538                        // $annot .= ' /S /D';        // style - [S]olid, [D]ashed, [B]eveled, [I]nset, [U]nderline
539                        // $annot .= ' /D [3 2]';        // Dash array - if dashed
540                        // $annot .= ' >>';
541                        // $annot .= ' /C [1 0 0]';    // Color RGB
542
543                        if ($this->mpdf->PDFA || $this->mpdf->PDFX) {
544                            $annot .= ' /F 28';
545                        }
546
547                        if (strpos($pl[4], '@') === 0) {
548
549                            $p = substr($pl[4], 1);
550                            // $h=isset($this->mpdf->OrientationChanges[$p]) ? $wPt : $hPt;
551                            $htarg = $this->mpdf->pageDim[$p]['h'] * Mpdf::SCALE;
552                            $annot .= sprintf(' /Dest [%d 0 R /XYZ 0 %.3F null]>>', 1 + 2 * $p, $htarg);
553
554                        } elseif (is_string($pl[4])) {
555
556                            $annot .= ' /A <</S /URI /URI ' . $this->writer->string($pl[4]) . '>> >>';
557
558                        } else {
559
560                            $l = $this->mpdf->links[$pl[4]];
561                            // may not be set if #link points to non-existent target
562                            if (isset($this->mpdf->pageDim[$l[0]]['h'])) {
563                                $htarg = $this->mpdf->pageDim[$l[0]]['h'] * Mpdf::SCALE;
564                            } else {
565                                $htarg = $this->mpdf->h * Mpdf::SCALE;
566                            } // doesn't really matter
567
568                            $annot .= sprintf(' /Dest [%d 0 R /XYZ 0 %.3F null]>>', 1 + 2 * $l[0], $htarg - $l[1] * Mpdf::SCALE);
569                        }
570
571                        $this->writer->write($annot);
572                        $this->writer->write('endobj');
573
574                    }
575                }
576
577                /* -- ANNOTATIONS -- */
578                if (isset($this->mpdf->PageAnnots[$n])) {
579
580                    foreach ($this->mpdf->PageAnnots[$n] as $key => $pl) {
581
582                        $fileAttachment = (bool) $pl['opt']['file'];
583
584                        if ($fileAttachment && !$this->mpdf->allowAnnotationFiles) {
585                            $this->logger->warning('Embedded files for annotations have to be allowed explicitly with "allowAnnotationFiles" config key');
586                            $fileAttachment = false;
587                        }
588
589                        $this->writer->object();
590
591                        $annot = '';
592                        $pl['opt'] = array_change_key_case($pl['opt'], CASE_LOWER);
593                        $x = $pl['x'];
594
595                        if ($this->mpdf->annotMargin != 0 || $x == 0 || $x < 0) { // Odd page, intentional non-strict comparison
596                            $x = ($wPt / Mpdf::SCALE) - $this->mpdf->annotMargin;
597                        }
598
599                        $w = $h = 0;
600                        $a = $x * Mpdf::SCALE;
601                        $b = $hPt - ($pl['y'] * Mpdf::SCALE);
602
603                        $annot .= '<</Type /Annot ';
604
605                        if ($fileAttachment) {
606                            $annot .= '/Subtype /FileAttachment ';
607                            // Need to set a size for FileAttachment icons
608                            if ($pl['opt']['icon'] === 'Paperclip') {
609                                $w = 8.235;
610                                $h = 20;
611                            } elseif ($pl['opt']['icon'] === 'Tag') {
612                                $w = 20;
613                                $h = 16;
614                            } elseif ($pl['opt']['icon'] === 'Graph') {
615                                $w = 20;
616                                $h = 20;
617                            } else {
618                                $w = 14;
619                                $h = 20;
620                            }
621
622                            // PushPin
623                            $f = $pl['opt']['file'];
624                            $f = preg_replace('/^.*\//', '', $f);
625                            $f = preg_replace('/[^a-zA-Z0-9._]/', '', $f);
626
627                            $annot .= '/FS <</Type /Filespec /F (' . $f . ')';
628                            $annot .= '/EF <</F ' . ($this->mpdf->n + 1) . ' 0 R>>';
629                            $annot .= '>>';
630
631                        } else {
632                            $annot .= '/Subtype /Text';
633                            $w = 20;
634                            $h = 20;  // mPDF 6
635                        }
636
637                        $rect = sprintf('%.3F %.3F %.3F %.3F', $a, $b - $h, $a + $w, $b);
638                        $annot .= ' /Rect [' . $rect . ']';
639
640                        // contents = description of file in free text
641                        $annot .= ' /Contents ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($pl['txt']);
642
643                        $annot .= ' /NM ' . $this->writer->string(sprintf('%04u-%04u', $n, 2000 + $key));
644                        $annot .= ' /M ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . date('YmdHis'));
645                        $annot .= ' /CreationDate ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . date('YmdHis'));
646                        $annot .= ' /Border [0 0 0]';
647
648                        if ($this->mpdf->PDFA || $this->mpdf->PDFX) {
649                            $annot .= ' /F 28';
650                            $annot .= ' /CA 1';
651                        } elseif ($pl['opt']['ca'] > 0) {
652                            $annot .= ' /CA ' . $pl['opt']['ca'];
653                        }
654
655                        $annotcolor = ' /C [';
656                        if (isset($pl['opt']['c']) && $pl['opt']['c']) {
657                            $col = $pl['opt']['c'];
658                            if ($col[0] == 3 || $col[0] == 5) {
659                                $annotcolor .= sprintf('%.3F %.3F %.3F', ord($col[1]) / 255, ord($col[2]) / 255, ord($col[3]) / 255);
660                            } elseif ($col[0] == 1) {
661                                $annotcolor .= sprintf('%.3F', ord($col[1]) / 255);
662                            } elseif ($col[0] == 4 || $col[0] == 6) {
663                                $annotcolor .= sprintf('%.3F %.3F %.3F %.3F', ord($col[1]) / 100, ord($col[2]) / 100, ord($col[3]) / 100, ord($col[4]) / 100);
664                            } else {
665                                $annotcolor .= '1 1 0';
666                            }
667                        } else {
668                            $annotcolor .= '1 1 0';
669                        }
670                        $annotcolor .= ']';
671                        $annot .= $annotcolor;
672
673                        // Usually Author
674                        // Use as Title for fileattachment
675                        if (isset($pl['opt']['t']) && is_string($pl['opt']['t'])) {
676                            $annot .= ' /T ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($pl['opt']['t']);
677                        }
678
679                        if ($fileAttachment) {
680                            $iconsapp = ['Paperclip', 'Graph', 'PushPin', 'Tag'];
681                        } else {
682                            $iconsapp = ['Comment', 'Help', 'Insert', 'Key', 'NewParagraph', 'Note', 'Paragraph'];
683                        }
684
685                        if (isset($pl['opt']['icon']) && in_array($pl['opt']['icon'], $iconsapp)) {
686                            $annot .= ' /Name /' . $pl['opt']['icon'];
687                        } elseif ($fileAttachment) {
688                            $annot .= ' /Name /PushPin';
689                        } else {
690                            $annot .= ' /Name /Note';
691                        }
692
693                        if (!$fileAttachment) {
694                            // Subj is PDF 1.5 spec.
695                            if (!$this->mpdf->PDFA && !$this->mpdf->PDFX && isset($pl['opt']['subj'])) {
696                                $annot .= ' /Subj ' . $this->writer->utf16BigEndianTextString($pl['opt']['subj']);
697                            }
698                            if (!empty($pl['opt']['popup'])) {
699                                $annot .= ' /Open true';
700                                $annot .= ' /Popup ' . ($this->mpdf->n + 1) . ' 0 R';
701                            } else {
702                                $annot .= ' /Open false';
703                            }
704                        }
705
706                        $annot .= ' /P ' . $pl['pageobj'] . ' 0 R';
707                        $annot .= '>>';
708                        $this->writer->write($annot);
709                        $this->writer->write('endobj');
710
711                        if ($fileAttachment) {
712
713                            $file = @file_get_contents($pl['opt']['file']);
714                            if (!$file) {
715                                throw new \Mpdf\MpdfException('mPDF Error: Cannot access file attachment - ' . $pl['opt']['file']);
716                            }
717
718                            $filestream = gzcompress($file);
719                            $this->writer->object();
720                            $this->writer->write('<</Type /EmbeddedFile');
721                            $this->writer->write('/Length ' . strlen($filestream));
722                            $this->writer->write('/Filter /FlateDecode');
723                            $this->writer->write('>>');
724                            $this->writer->stream($filestream);
725                            $this->writer->write('endobj');
726
727                        } elseif (!empty($pl['opt']['popup'])) {
728                            $this->writer->object();
729                            $annot = '';
730                            if (is_array($pl['opt']['popup']) && isset($pl['opt']['popup'][0])) {
731                                $x = $pl['opt']['popup'][0] * Mpdf::SCALE;
732                            } else {
733                                $x = $pl['x'] * Mpdf::SCALE;
734                            }
735                            if (is_array($pl['opt']['popup']) && isset($pl['opt']['popup'][1])) {
736                                $y = $hPt - ($pl['opt']['popup'][1] * Mpdf::SCALE);
737                            } else {
738                                $y = $hPt - ($pl['y'] * Mpdf::SCALE);
739                            }
740                            if (is_array($pl['opt']['popup']) && isset($pl['opt']['popup'][2])) {
741                                $w = $pl['opt']['popup'][2] * Mpdf::SCALE;
742                            } else {
743                                $w = 180;
744                            }
745                            if (is_array($pl['opt']['popup']) && isset($pl['opt']['popup'][3])) {
746                                $h = $pl['opt']['popup'][3] * Mpdf::SCALE;
747                            } else {
748                                $h = 120;
749                            }
750                            $rect = sprintf('%.3F %.3F %.3F %.3F', $x, $y - $h, $x + $w, $y);
751                            $annot .= '<</Type /Annot /Subtype /Popup /Rect [' . $rect . ']';
752                            $annot .= ' /M ' . $this->writer->string('D:' . date('YmdHis'));
753                            if ($this->mpdf->PDFA || $this->mpdf->PDFX) {
754                                $annot .= ' /F 28';
755                            }
756                            $annot .= ' /Parent ' . ($this->mpdf->n - 1) . ' 0 R';
757                            $annot .= '>>';
758                            $this->writer->write($annot);
759                            $this->writer->write('endobj');
760                        }
761                    }
762                }
763
764                // Active Forms
765                if (count($this->form->forms) > 0) {
766                    $this->form->_putFormItems($n, $hPt);
767                }
768            }
769        }
770
771        // Active Forms - Radio Button Group entries
772        // Output Radio Button Group form entries (radio_on_obj_id already determined)
773        if (count($this->form->form_radio_groups)) {
774            $this->form->_putRadioItems($n);
775        }
776    }

778    public function writeEncryption() // _putencryption
779    {
780        $this->writer->write('/Filter /Standard');
781        if ($this->protection->getUseRC128Encryption()) {
782            $this->writer->write('/V 2');
783            $this->writer->write('/R 3');
784            $this->writer->write('/Length 128');
785        } else {
786            $this->writer->write('/V 1');
787            $this->writer->write('/R 2');
788        }

809    private function getVersionString()
810    {
811        $return = Mpdf::VERSION;
812        $headFile = __DIR__ . '/../../.git/HEAD';
813        if (file_exists($headFile)) {
814            $ref = file($headFile);
815            $path = explode('/', $ref[0], 3);
816            $branch = isset($path[2]) ? trim($path[2]) : '';
817            $revFile = __DIR__ . '/../../.git/refs/heads/' . $branch;
818            if ($branch && file_exists($revFile)) {
819                $rev = file($revFile);
820                $rev = substr($rev[0], 0, 7);
821                $return .= ' (' . $rev . ')';
822            }
823        }
824
825        return $return;
826    }
